text: Helga Braathen (5 March 1953 – 11 October 1982) was a Norwegian artistic gymnast. She was born in Drammen. She competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics. She died 29 years old suffering from anorexia nervosa. == References == == External links == * Category:1953 births Category:People from Drammen Category:Norwegian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:1982 deaths
